                    "body": "Agreed with Benjamin and Dolf. The current behavior is considered buggy, so we break BC slightly. All such breaks should include a \"migration\" chapter in the relevant documentation indicating what the break is, why it occurred, and how to update the code.\n\nRobin -- this would not be considered something that falls under feature freeze; if you cannot get it in by feature freeze tomorrow, you can still merge it to the release branch prior to the RC.",
